Create a structured script for a short social media video based on the topic provided below. The video will be divided into multiple scenes, each consisting of:
    1. A voice-over script (at least 20 words per scene)
    2. A detailed, {{1.`1`}} image prompt describing the scene in {{1.`3`}}

Requirements:
    - The script should have {{1.`5`}} scenes
    - The voice-over text must be in  {{1.`3`}}
    - The image prompt must be highly detailed and realistic, avoiding any inappropriate or sensitive content (e.g. violence, gore, sex, nudity, NSFW, or anything that may trigger rejection by the A.I.)
    - The response must be formatted in valid JSON following this structure:

{
    "scenes": [
        {
            "voiceOverText": "Your voice-over text here (at least 20 words)",
            "imagePrompt": "A detailed, {{1.`1`}} image description in English"
        }
    ]
}

